Get custom labels.

Returns:
    dict: Label list info.
        e.g.:
            {
                "projectNameList": [
                    {
                        "projectId": 3671,
                        "projectName": "myLabel"
                    }
                ]
            }

Get custom labels.

Returns:
    list: Label list info.
        e.g.:
            [
                {
                    "projectId": 3671,
                    "projectName": "myLabel"
                }
            ]

Get the project name based on the flag.

Args:
    flag (int): 0. Query items under this account;
                1. Query items under this account and under the master account;
                2. Query all items associated with (all items under the same master account)

Get platforms.

Returns:
    list: Platforms info.
        e.g.:
             [
                 {
                     "platform": 2,
                     "name": "query_platform_w2"
                 },
             ]

Get supported rendering software plugins.

Args:
    name (str): The name of the DCC.
        e.g.:
            maya,
            houdini
    os_name (str): Os name, the default is based on the current system.
        e.g.:
            windows

Returns:
    dict: Plugin info.
        e.g.:
            {
                "cgPlugin": [
                    {
                        "cvId": 19,
                        "pluginName": "zblur",
                        "pluginVersions": [
                            {
                                "pluginId": 1652,
                                "pluginName": "zblur",
                                "pluginVersion": "zblur 2.02.019"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                ],
                "cgVersion": [
                    {
                        "id": 23,
                        "cgId": 2005,
                        "cgName": "CINEMA 4D",
                        "cgVersion": "R19"
                    }
                ]
            }

